  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/1ab4004031911fb726221054c1d5e318.avif?t=1757457201\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3XTINCTION is an Online Co-op Top Down Shooter with tactical and strategic elements. After a series of experiments on spiders gone wrong, the world is devasted by an outbreak. Prepare yourself before every wave, buy weapons, ammos and set up turrets to stay alive. Each wave, the Infecteds are more and more numerous.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ONLINE COOPERATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is fully playable online for 2 players. You and your friend will have to cooperate in order to complete missions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/5bc78519c90be184a11dab50f340fc54.poster.avif?t=1757457201\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/5bc78519c90be184a11dab50f340fc54.webm?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/5bc78519c90be184a11dab50f340fc54.mp4?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CONSTRUCTIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare yourself before every wave, buy constructions like turrets, decoy and barbed wires, place them freely on the levels !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/c0b179787bc64629ec9939145abe324d.poster.avif?t=1757457201\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/c0b179787bc64629ec9939145abe324d.webm?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/c0b179787bc64629ec9939145abe324d.mp4?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CLASS SYSTEM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 3XTINCTION Cooperation is key to survival, choose between 5 different class with unique skills and equipments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/f97d882046577398a0dfa06fb8746196.avif?t=1757457201\" width=610 height=342 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPGRADE YOUR WEAPONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In case of zombie invasion, it's important to be well-armed! Use the money you've earned to buy new weapons and upgrade them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/4488e3d1954158fdde3bc1d5cc7c629f.poster.avif?t=1757457201\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/4488e3d1954158fdde3bc1d5cc7c629f.webm?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/4488e3d1954158fdde3bc1d5cc7c629f.mp4?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SELECT YOU CHARACTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just because it's the apocalypse doesn't mean we can't have a good time! Use the money you've earned to unlock new stylish characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/d3dd80017c61c81f38ba9a217560e2fc.poster.avif?t=1757457201\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/d3dd80017c61c81f38ba9a217560e2fc.webm?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/d3dd80017c61c81f38ba9a217560e2fc.mp4?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SKILLS SYSTEM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't want to be ripped apart by zombies, think about upgrading your skills! Spend XP tokens earned to unlock new skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/7d5043c96c14542eff85bced887d1eb7.avif?t=1757457201\" width=610 height=342 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Cooperative Online gameplay for up to 2 players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 8 different type of missions </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Use and upgrade more than 15 weapons to fight the outbreak. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Complete missions in 7 different locations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Choose between 6 different class with unique skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Solo game mode with BOTS</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/1ab4004031911fb726221054c1d5e318.avif?t=1757457201\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3XTINCTION is an Online Co-op Top Down Shooter with tactical and strategic elements. After a series of experiments on spiders gone wrong, the world is devasted by an outbreak. Prepare yourself before every wave, buy weapons, ammos and set up turrets to stay alive. Each wave, the Infecteds are more and more numerous.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ONLINE COOPERATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is fully playable online for 2 players. You and your friend will have to cooperate in order to complete missions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/5bc78519c90be184a11dab50f340fc54.poster.avif?t=1757457201\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/5bc78519c90be184a11dab50f340fc54.webm?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/5bc78519c90be184a11dab50f340fc54.mp4?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CONSTRUCTIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare yourself before every wave, buy constructions like turrets, decoy and barbed wires, place them freely on the levels !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/c0b179787bc64629ec9939145abe324d.poster.avif?t=1757457201\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/c0b179787bc64629ec9939145abe324d.webm?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/c0b179787bc64629ec9939145abe324d.mp4?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CLASS SYSTEM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 3XTINCTION Cooperation is key to survival, choose between 5 different class with unique skills and equipments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/f97d882046577398a0dfa06fb8746196.avif?t=1757457201\" width=610 height=342 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPGRADE YOUR WEAPONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In case of zombie invasion, it's important to be well-armed! Use the money you've earned to buy new weapons and upgrade them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/4488e3d1954158fdde3bc1d5cc7c629f.poster.avif?t=1757457201\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/4488e3d1954158fdde3bc1d5cc7c629f.webm?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/4488e3d1954158fdde3bc1d5cc7c629f.mp4?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SELECT YOU CHARACTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just because it's the apocalypse doesn't mean we can't have a good time! Use the money you've earned to unlock new stylish characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/d3dd80017c61c81f38ba9a217560e2fc.poster.avif?t=1757457201\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/d3dd80017c61c81f38ba9a217560e2fc.webm?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/d3dd80017c61c81f38ba9a217560e2fc.mp4?t=1757457201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SKILLS SYSTEM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't want to be ripped apart by zombies, think about upgrading your skills! Spend XP tokens earned to unlock new skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564630/extras/7d5043c96c14542eff85bced887d1eb7.avif?t=1757457201\" width=610 height=342 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Cooperative Online gameplay for up to 2 players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 8 different type of missions </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Use and upgrade more than 15 weapons to fight the outbreak. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Complete missions in 7 different locations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Choose between 6 different class with unique skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Solo game mode with BOTS</p>",
